OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy start, though
OL,6,Fwith a few sunny intervals. Cloud
OL,7,Fbreaking up through the course of the
OL,8,Fday to give plenty of long sunny
OL,9,Fspells. Dry and feeling warm in the
OL,10,Fsunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry evening with plenty of
OL,13,Flate evening sunshine on offer, but
OL,14,Fcloudier for coastal areas of Argyll.
OL,15,FRemaining dry overnight with mostly
OL,16,Fclear skies but cloudier around the
OL,17,Fcoasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
