OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA dry day and mostly cloudy
OL,6,Fnear the coasts with some bright or
OL,7,Fsunny intervals. Further inland will
OL,8,Fsee clearer skies and plenty of
OL,9,Fsunshine, feeling warm here.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,12,Flargely dry and settled few days with
OL,13,Fthe odd spot of rain possible at
OL,14,Ftimes. Cloudy at times but still
OL,15,Fplenty of bright or sunny spells on
OL,16,Foffer.
